309
00:16:53,472 --> 00:16:55,272
Do you care that much about Fang Lili?

310
00:16:55,911 --> 00:16:57,112
I don't care about her.

311
00:16:57,311 --> 00:16:58,512
She's just more useful.

312
00:17:05,672 --> 00:17:06,992
I'll revise the document.

313
00:17:08,111 --> 00:17:09,591
It'll be done by tomorrow if lucky.

314
00:17:46,032 --> 00:17:47,272
Where to? I'll drive.

315
00:17:52,032 --> 00:17:53,591
This is at the company's entrance.

316
00:17:56,032 --> 00:17:58,032
Hurry and get in, then no one will see.

317
00:18:12,311 --> 00:18:13,432
Please enjoy your coffee.

318
00:18:19,151 --> 00:18:20,591
Back when we were at school,

319
00:18:20,712 --> 00:18:21,992
