370
00:21:11,672 --> 00:21:12,912
that you'll listen to her,

371
00:21:13,032 --> 00:21:14,351
and live a good life.

372
00:21:20,071 --> 00:21:20,831
Say something.

373
00:21:21,591 --> 00:21:22,591
Tell Lili to stay.

374
00:21:33,631 --> 00:21:34,472
Grandma,

375
00:21:35,192 --> 00:21:37,192
when I was homeless,

376
00:21:37,192 --> 00:21:38,752
An Yushen took me in.

377
00:21:39,071 --> 00:21:39,952
