400
00:23:24,232 --> 00:23:26,791
Why didn't you ask Lili to stay?

401
00:23:27,992 --> 00:23:29,391
Don't you love her anymore?

402
00:23:34,391 --> 00:23:36,032
Since you still love her,

403
00:23:36,311 --> 00:23:37,551
