404
00:23:39,071 --> 00:23:40,551
Are you afraid she doesn't love you?

405
00:23:42,712 --> 00:23:44,272
I am afraid that she does love me.

406
00:23:44,831 --> 00:23:46,512
Are you writing poetry here?

407
00:23:47,551 --> 00:23:49,351
What are you being so sentimental about?

408
00:23:51,151 --> 00:23:51,871
Grandma,

409
00:23:52,232 --> 00:23:54,351
