410
00:23:54,351 --> 00:23:55,111
then she...

411
00:23:57,952 --> 00:23:59,071
I can't explain clearly.

412
00:23:59,791 --> 00:24:01,192
Then you don't need to explain.

413
00:24:02,351 --> 00:24:03,151
Yushen,

414
00:24:04,631 --> 00:24:06,752
you have made rapid progress recently,

415
00:24:06,992 --> 00:24:08,272
but I know

416
00:24:08,551 --> 00:24:11,192
you've never been clever
since you were little.

417
00:24:12,272 --> 00:24:13,591
Lili is so capable.

418
00:24:14,512 --> 00:24:15,672
I hope

419
00:24:15,672 --> 00:24:17,391
that someone can take care of you.

420
00:24:19,032 --> 00:24:19,631
Grandma,

421
00:24:21,192 --> 00:24:22,672
but I hope to take care of her.

422
00:24:23,952 --> 00:24:25,232
I don't know how to do it.

