An Yushen back out.

445
00:26:58,071 --> 00:26:59,472
Is this your choice?

446
00:26:59,871 --> 00:27:00,512
Yes.

447
00:27:18,712 --> 00:27:19,512
Fang Li,

448
00:27:23,791 --> 00:27:25,032
