452
00:27:32,791 --> 00:27:34,151
I will smash it open and get out.

453
00:27:34,272 --> 00:27:35,111
It won't work.

454
00:27:35,192 --> 00:27:36,111
I've tried.

455
00:27:40,351 --> 00:27:41,151
Fang Li,

456
00:27:42,791 --> 00:27:43,871
you don't want to face it,

457
00:27:44,432 --> 00:27:45,272
neither do I.

458
00:27:45,871 --> 00:27:47,831
But shall we just pretend
this didn't happen?

459
00:27:48,871 --> 00:27:50,192
Then what do you want me to do?

460
00:27:51,192 --> 00:27:52,631
I still can't believe

461
00:27:52,631 --> 00:27:54,591
something so ridiculous actually
happened to me.

462
00:27:54,952 --> 00:27:56,631
I'm trapped in an invisible,

463
00:27:56,631 --> 00:27:57,871
intangible wall.

464
00:27:57,871 --> 00:28:00,111
The only way out is to trap you here.

465
00:28:01,472 --> 00:28:02,672
I don't know what to do.

466
00:28:02,672 --> 00:28:03,151
I...

467
00:28:04,151 --> 00:28:05,871
I just feel so useless.

468
00:28:13,912 --> 00:28:15,391
If you are useless,

469
00:28:16,111 --> 00:28:17,311
