476
00:28:30,952 --> 00:28:32,272
You're in this reality.

477
00:28:35,071 --> 00:28:35,712
Fang Li,

478
00:28:37,311 --> 00:28:38,551
I won't run away again.

479
00:28:39,071 --> 00:28:40,032
Let's go out together.

480
00:28:41,071 --> 00:28:42,631
