481
00:28:43,791 --> 00:28:44,591
I definitely can.

482
00:28:44,591 --> 00:28:45,432
Trust me.

483
00:28:49,752 --> 00:28:50,512
Idiot.

484
00:28:53,391 --> 00:28:54,551
You're smarter than me.

485
00:28:54,831 --> 00:28:56,672
Simply do what you should,
and you can get out.

486
00:28:57,952 --> 00:28:59,111
If you didn't try saving me,

487
00:28:59,391 --> 00:29:00,391
you'd have been out.

488
00:29:01,791 --> 00:29:02,631
You're foolish,

489
00:29:02,912 --> 00:29:03,752
and so am I.

490
00:29:04,631 --> 00:29:05,791
What are you trying to say?

491
00:29:08,551 --> 00:29:09,432
I want to tell you

492
00:29:10,871 --> 00:29:11,912
to trust me.

493
00:29:12,071 --> 00:29:12,591
I...

494
00:29:15,071 --> 00:29:16,032
