505
00:31:08,616 --> 00:31:12,866
♪I don't dare to reminisce♪

506
00:31:12,866 --> 00:31:16,519
♪For fear that tears fill my eyes♪

507
00:31:16,872 --> 00:31:20,419
♪I can't return to the past
and embrace you♪

508
00:31:20,725 --> 00:31:22,920
♪It's already in vain♪

509
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:26,472
♪I stood alone under the street light♪

